<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="resolve-v">resolve <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'zɒlv/    美 /rɪ'zɑːlv/  </p>
<p>[正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-settle">1.★ <strong>解决 (settle)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>resolve a conflict / an issue</strong> / difficulties
解决冲突/解决问题/解决难题</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[正式用语] 决心；决定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Instead of <strong>resolving to lose</strong> weight, try an actionable resolution: “I’ll stop having dessert for lunch.”  
不要光下决心减肥，要尝试一个可行性的决心：“我午餐不再吃甜品。”</p><footer>2014 北京改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>resolution /ˌrezə'luːʃn/ n [C] &amp; [U]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>conflict resolution
冲突解决</p></div></div>